=== PEAR packages needed for the RFC system to work ===

DB
HTML_QuickForm
Mail
HTML_BBCodeParser
Text_Wiki

== Installation ===

pear install DB
pear install Mail
pear install HTML_QuickForm
pear install HTML_BBCodeParser
pear install -f Text_Wiki

or all at ones (latest releases)

pear install -f DB Mail HTML_QuickForm HTML_BBCodeParser Text_Wiki



